        li <strong>Image Search</strong>: Searches Google Images for a user-provided term (<em>/imagesearch/search/&lt;term&gt;</em>). Shows the last searches on <em>/imagesearch/lastest</em>. <a href="/imagesearch">Click here: <em>/imagesearch</em></a>
